subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams was the lone top-10 player who remained in the top half of the women’s draw. Kei Nishikori fell in the men’s bracket. Other first-round victims included Ana Ivanovic and Carla Suárez Navarro.
